1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,800
Here's what science actually says about prebiotics.

2
00:00:02,800 --> 00:00:07,200
Prebiotics are types of fiber that feed your good gut bacteria.

3
00:00:07,200 --> 00:00:11,200
Without them, your microbiome can struggle, leading to digestive issues.

4
00:00:11,200 --> 00:00:15,200
Studies show prebiotics can improve gut health and boost immunity.

5
00:00:15,200 --> 00:00:19,200
But here's the twist: not all prebiotics are created equal!

6
00:00:19,200 --> 00:00:24,000
Some early research suggests that the wrong types can actually cause bloating.

7
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:27,200
Want to unlock the secrets of gut health?

8
00:00:27,200 --> 00:00:28,800
Follow for more insights!
